    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with plenty of life left for the right buyer. This car shows cosmetic wear consistent with age and use, but it remains a straightforward, mechanically simple platform with dependable transportation potential. The powertrain pulls cleanly, the chassis feels composed, and it would make an excellent commuter, first car, or light project for someone who appreciates a usable vehicle over showroom polish. If you want an affordable car with practical value and room to improve, this one is worth a look.",
