      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with loads of character, this car has the kind of presence that turns an ordinary driveway into the start of a story. It\u2019s an ideal find for someone who loves the charm of a well-traveled machine and sees the opportunity in giving a classic daily driver its next chapter. Whether you\u2019re after a budget-friendly runabout, a hands-on project, or a unique vehicle with personality you just can\u2019t fake, this one brings plenty of potential and unmistakable soul.",
      "price": 6200.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "A straightforward, budget-friendly vehicle that offers practical transportation at an accessible price. This car shows its age and is best suited for someone seeking dependable basic use, a project opportunity, or an inexpensive second vehicle. Presented with honest value in mind, it stands out as a cost-conscious choice for buyers who prioritize affordability and utility.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels without spending a fortune? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great opportunity for someone who wants cheap, usable transportation or a solid little project. It has the kind of honest character you expect at this price point, and it could suit a first-time buyer, commuter, or handy owner who doesn\u2019t mind giving it a bit of TLC. If you want something budget-friendly with potential, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid project or budget daily with a strong-running powertrain and plenty of usable life left. Starts up, drives, and has the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes it easy to wrench on and inexpensive to keep on the road. Not a cosmetic showpiece, but the drivetrain feels willing, the chassis is honest, and it would make a great commuter, first car, or enthusiast project for someone who appreciates a straightforward platform. A lot of value here for the money if you want dependable basic transportation with room to improve.",
